          Title: First Light and Reionization: A Conference Summary
          Authors:  E. J. Barton, J. S. Bullock, A. Cooray, M. Kaplinghat
          (UC Irvine)
          Comments:  to  appear  in  the  proceedings  of  the  UC Irvine
