astro-ph/0512118 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :

          Title:  Kinematics and star formation activity in the z=2.03954
          damped Lyman-alpha system towards PKS 0458-020
          Authors:  Janine Heinmueller, Patrick Petitjean, Cedric Ledoux,
          Sara Caucci, R. Srianand
          Comments: accepted for publication in A&A
