          We  report  the  discoveries  of two, two-image gravitationally
          lensed quasars selected from the Sloan Digital Sky Survey: SDSS
          J0806+2006  at  z_s=1.540 and SDSS J1353+1138 at z_s=1.629 with
          image    separations   of   1.40"   and   1.41"   respectively.
