          Title: Elemental Abundance Survey of The Galactic Thick Disk
          Authors:  Bacham  E.  Reddy  (1),  David L. Lambert (2), Carlos
          Allende  Prieto  (2)  ((1)  IIA, Bangalore, (2) Univ. of Texas,
          Austin)
