          galaxies analogous to the Local Group. The survey was conducted
          using  the Parkes telescope and the Australia Telescope Compact
          Array  to  produce  a  census  of all the gas-rich galaxies and
          potential  analogs  to  the  high-velocity clouds (HVCs) within
          these  groups  down to M(HI)<10^7 M(sun) as a test of models of
