          Chandra  X-ray  error  circle.  Both are substantially reddened
          being  consistent  with  the patchy interstellar absorption. We
          will discuss the nature of this source in the framework of what
          is currently known about optical counterparts of ULXs.


   
astro-ph/0603771 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
