          (1),  Matthias  Kadler  (2),  Eduardo Ros (2), Merja Tornikoski
          (3),  Margo  F.  Aller  (4),  Hugh  D.  Aller  (4)  ((1) Tuorla
          Observatory,  University  of  Turku,  Finland  (2) MPIfR, Bonn,
