          derived  from integrated spectra and stellar population models.
          Standard   techniques   may   give   rise  to  spuriously  high
          alpha-element  ratios  at  low  metallicities.  We then discuss
          evidence  for  early  epoch  (z  > 2) formation for most GCs in
