          Title: Spitzer Quasar and ULIRG evolution study (QUEST): I. The
          origin of the far infrared continuum of QSOs
          Authors:  M.  Schweitzer,  D. Lutz, E. Sturm, A. Contursi, L.J.
          Tacconi,  M.D.  Lehnert,  K. Dasyra, R. Genzel, S. Veilleux, D.
