          outgoing  radiation  pressure,  suggest nucleation of hexagonal
          sheets  from  pentagons, perhaps from a supercooled melt. These
          results warrant a closer examination of specimen structure, the
          energetics of unlayered graphene nucleation, and processes such
          as jets in late star atmospheres.


   
