          Title:  The  Direct  Detection of Lyman-Continuum Emission from
          Star-forming Galaxies at z~3
          Authors:  Alice  E.  Shapley  (Princeton),  Charles  C. Steidel
          (Caltech),  Max  Pettini  (IoA), Kurt L. Adelberger (McKinsey &
