          characteristics   of   the   PG  1004+130  jet,  including  its
          relatively  flat  X-ray  power  law and concave spectral energy
          distribution,  are similar to those of powerful FR II jets. The
          lack  of strong beaming in PG 1004+130 limits the efficiency of
