          We  examine  the  evolution  of  the IGM Ly-alpha optical depth
          distribution    using    the   transmitted   flux   probability
          distribution  function  (PDF)  in  a sample of 63 QSOs spanning
          absorption  redshifts  1.7  < z < 5.8. The data are compared to
          two   theoretical   optical   depth   distributions:   a  model
          distribution    based    on   the   density   distribution   of
