          Title:  Cosmology  at Low Frequencies: The 21 cm Transition and
          the High-Redshift Universe
          Authors:  Steven  Furlanetto  (Yale),  S. Peng Oh (UCSB), Frank
          Briggs (RSAA and ATNF)
          Comments:  extended  review  accepted  by  Physics Reports, 207
          pages,  44  figures  (some  low  resolution); version with high
